# Harmony patches

- Patch types in `Features/{Feature}/Patches/*.cs` (one file per patched game type)
- `AccessTools.Method`/`Field` over string literals when target type is known
- `TargetMethod()` must return valid `MethodBase` or Harmony fails silently
- Confirm signatures in `deps/decompiled/**/*` before patching
- try/catch in patch bodies; `ModLog.Warn(Feature, …)` — do not swallow silently
- Registration, discovery, config, logging: [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md)
